author: David Fischer
title: Nike Debuts The Minimal Air Max Thea Ultra Flyknit for 2017
text:
Visit the original post to see all 4 images from this gallery. 
Nike rings in the New Year with a strong new iteration of the Nike Air Max Thea. The modern icon returns in a new lightweight and minimal Ultra Flyknit version. The Flyknit material delivers breathability and support exactly where you need it, and a cored-out Ultra midsole provides the soft cushioning you need without added weight. The sneaker drops today, January 1, 2017, in an oreo colorway and a black/red version as well on Nike.com .
